<item rdf:about="https://medical.nikkeibp.co.jp/leaf/mem/pub/search/cancer/news/202210/576865.html">
<title>FGFR阻害薬フチバチニブが米国でFGFR2遺伝子融合または再構成を有する進行肝内胆管癌を対象に承認</title>
<link>https://medical.nikkeibp.co.jp/leaf/mem/pub/search/cancer/news/202210/576865.html</link>
